snippet.title: Dota Underlords Season One Trailer
snippet.description:
SEASON ONE NOW AVAILABLE
Dota Underlords Season One comes with a City to explore, a Battle Pass full of rewards, and multiple ways to play. Dota Underlords is now out of Early Access and ready to play!

Visit http://www.underlords.com for more info
